Then open the new `.env` file in any text editor. It should look like this — **no changes needed if MongoDB is running locally**:
```
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development

MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/adaptlearn

JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_jwt_key_change_this_in_production
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d

CLIENT_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:5500